{"tid":2517852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈, 印度已經亡國","createTime":"2021-05-05T14:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T14:53:34.000Z","uid":353278,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"b20f4eefc6b19d305fe0b98c9fe6684c6af13247","tid":2517852,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:43:01.000Z","msg":"covid 19 係血管病, 主要破壞係引致血管栓塞, 主要症狀其實係中風. 就算所謂好返都有腦部被破壞, 唔少所謂康復者醫返都得返半條人命<br />\n正式埋單印度可能超過五成人口奶過嘢, 到時要養住一大班冇咗半條命嘅人....<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">印度已經亡國</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAccording to one study published in the Annals of Clinical and Translational Neurology, <strong><em><ins>85 of the 100 patients</ins></em></strong> examined experienced at least four or more neurological effects following their diagnosis. These symptoms included brain fog, headaches, numbness/tingling, muscle pain, and dizziness.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We&rsquo;ve been seeing a lot of the neurological disorders,&rdquo; Dr. Suzanne Judd, a professor at the University of Alabama at Birmingham School of Public Health, told Yahoo Finance. &ldquo;When COVID first hit, the people were talking about the cardiac conditions or heart conditions, but now we&rsquo;re starting to hear more and more talk about stroke and other neurological diseases, [and] some of the blood clot disorders, like blood clots in the legs and in the lungs.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The interesting thing about stroke [is] if it does have something to do with blood clots, your heart can throw really tiny clots into your brain,&rdquo; Judd said. &ldquo;That leads to all kinds of conditions afterwards &mdash; memory loss, full-on stroke where one side of your body can lose the ability to open bottles and move, lose the ability to communicate and the ability to understand, and all of those things wind up being associated with mental health.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/coronavirus-neurological-issues-covid-19-132123872.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2Fcoronavirus-neurological-issues-covid-19-132123872.html&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mn6tywrPEU2nSstxgUPIv8k8%3D&h=e495dbb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.yahoo.com/news/coronavirus-neurological-issues-covid-19-132123872.html</a>"},{"pid":"f41cde5ea2060ab63d62df580f03102cb1cf0a1f","tid":2517852,"uid":136061,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:43:46.000Z","msg":"自作孽"},{"pid":"21961d3701f83dcf7d2e1c7d0c5cbdb2e3429bad","tid":2517852,"uid":30868,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:44:06.000Z","msg":"信陳雲，弱感冒"},{"pid":"e630dffce866d3ebf83718fc13e4d28298815120","tid":2517852,"uid":169741,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:44:35.000Z","msg":"係外國做IT狗既人既喜訊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1870b9cbb29d194bd6876cd3456b84040ebfd0cb","tid":2517852,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:46:02.000Z","msg":"核平印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e965193d1796c41653ae154ffa299dd5e02b8bd7","tid":2517852,"uid":239912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:46:40.000Z","msg":"恆河都唔夠打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d2809a889f4194a478824c1da593a774260ed3e","tid":2517852,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"無得返印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b075496660bd8f0cb76a3d45f11fe64ca322093c","tid":2517852,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T14:48:10.000Z","msg":"翠翠統戰成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi